high_descs: Turn left, turn left and walk towards the door, turn right at the door, walk to the garbage bag straight ahead, turn right to face the table.
Pick up the sharp knife in front of the salt shaker.
Turn and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge door, put the knife in the fridge in the mug,
Pick up the mug from the fridge, close the fridge door.
Turn and walk to the counter to the left of the stove.
Put the mug down on the counter.
anns.task_desc: To put a knife in the chilled mug and put the knife on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and move to the fridge, then head right to the trash bag in the corner, and when you get there, face the table.
Pick up the sharp knife with the yellow handle from the table.
Turn right and carry the knife to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the knife in the white mug.
Pick up the white mug with the knife inside from the fridge.
Turn and move to the counter space to the left of the stove.
Place the mug with the knife in it on the counter left of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Move a knife in a mug to the counter by the stove.

high_descs: Turn around, go forward to the door, turn right, go forward to the trash bag, turn right to the table.
Take the large knife from the table.
Turn right, go forward to the fridge.
Put the knife in the mug in the fridge.
Take the mug from the fridge.
Turn left, go forward, at the sink turn left, go forward to the table, turn right, go forward to the counter to the left of the oven.
Put the mug on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a knife in it on a counter.
